reviewText: It was a good season, but I was expecting more action since the last ones had a lot. This felt like it went back a few steps, like from seasons 1-4. BUT it seems like the action we want will be coming in with the next season! (or so we hope).

Title: Red Vs. Blue Season 11

reviewText: Season 1 was corny, but funny.  Seasons 2-8 just kept getting slightly better and better.  I love this series!When I watched season 9 I was amazed at the graphics they were using.  They were finally using their own CGI!Season 10 was EPIC!  I  watched season 10 all 3 days of my 3 day rental.  It was THAT good!  I could not wait for season 11 to come out, so instead of watch the mini episodes on their website, I waited for the year to finish and rented the whole episode.I can't believe I paid for this!!!!  Not only is it 40 minutes shorter than season 10, but they used ZERO CGI!!!!  Why are they going backwards!!!!  And they left the season short!!!!  This is BS!!!  What a waste of a year!!!!  I want my money back!!!!
Title: Red Vs. Blue Season 11

reviewText: Another hilarious installment in the best web series ever... of all time.

reviewText: This definitly gets back to what made red vs blue so good.  Focus on good one liners and the normal stuff it seems sarge, griff, cabose, and all the others do to each other.  Seeing lopez come back and the way they kept the joke going was good and new.

reviewText: season 11 is up to par with previous seasons of red vs blue, and i highly recommend getting this season as well. it starts a new chapter with our favorite heroes, with the exception of Church and Carolina but that's only due to a story/plot line. i get the feeling we will see them again soon =)
